        <p>Cloudfox will provide the Services to you at the rates and for the fees (“Fees”) described on the Pricing page. The Fees include charges for Transactions (such as processing a payment) and for other events connected with your Cloudfox Account (such as handling a disputed charge). We may revise the Fees at any time. However, we will provide you with at least 30 days’ advance notice before revisions become applicable to you (or a longer period of notice if this is required by applicable Law).
