        <p>We will provide you with support to resolve general issues relating to your Cloudfox Account and your use of the Services. This support includes resources and documentation that we make available to you through the current versions of Cloudfox’s support pages, API documentation, and other pages on our website (collectively, “Documentation”). The most efficient way to get answers to your questions is to review our Documentation. If you still have questions after reviewing the Documentation, please contact us.</p>
