        <p>a. Consent to Electronic Disclosures and Notices: By registering for a Cloudfox Account, you agree that such registration constitutes your electronic signature, and you consent to electronic provision of all disclosures and notices from Cloudfox (“Notices”), including those required by Law. You also agree that your electronic consent will have the same legal effect as a physical signature.</p>
        
