        <p>By communicating with CLOUDFOX, you hereby agree that your communications may be monitored and recorded without previous notice. We may also collect your data by other means, for example, your answers to surveys, and interactions with other companies (subject to these companies’ privacy policies and applicable legislation).</p>
        
